claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A partial page of a clinical document showing a legend defining vaccine abbreviations (RIV4: Flublok; SD-IIV4: various egg-based vaccines) and text discussing comparative vaccine effectiveness (rVE) for different influenza vaccines in adults. The image only presents vaccine abbreviations and comparative effectiveness data; it does not address antigenic composition or affirm that Flublok matches WHO- and FDA-selected strains, and therefore does not support the claim. Note: Image is a partial excerpt and does not include information on antigenic match.
